<html>
	<head>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="/js/roomname_email.js"></script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<br />
		<br />
		The below is the Info of the Token Adam gives you to his account (maybe not full access though):
		<br />
		<hr style="border: 1px #B0C4DE solid;width:70%;" align="left"/>
		<br />
		<br />
		Access Token: <%=tokenInfo.access_token%>
		<br /><br />
		It expires in: <%=tokenInfo.expires_in%>
		<br /><br />
		Refresh Token: <%=tokenInfo.refresh_token%>
		<br /><br />
		It expires in: <%=tokenInfo.refresh_token_expires_in%>
		<br />
		<br />
		<br />
		<hr style="border: 1px #B0C4DE solid;width:70%;" align="left"/>
		<br />
		<br />
		Now, let's use the Access Token to create a room so that you can chat with him: 
		<br /><br />
		<hr style="border: 1px #B0C4DE solid;width:70%;" align="left"/>
		<form action="/actions/createAndJoinRoom" method="post">
			<br /><br />
			Room Name: <input type="text" name="roomName" value="Rock Spark Room"/> (Be used as room name, 2~20 characters. No special character allowed)
			<br /><br />
			Your Email: <input type="text" name="userEmail" value="Your own email"/> (Be used to add you into the room)
			<br /><br />
			<input type="submit" value="submit"/>
		</form>
		<br />
		<hr style="border: 1px #B0C4DE solid;width:70%;" align="left"/>
		<br />
		<br />
		<br />
	</body>
</html>